{"word":"Abigail","slug":"abigail","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abigail</b> <a href=\"#/H26\">H26</a> <br/> 1. Nabal's wife<br/> - Her wisdom and tact, and marriage to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25'>1Sa 25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=3'>1Sa 27:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=2'>2Sa 2:2</a> <br/> - Mother of Chileab by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ch 3:1</a> <br/> - Taken captive and rescued by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=18'>1Sa 30:18</a> <br/> 2. Sister of David and mother of Amasa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=25'>2Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=17'>1Ch 2:17</a>"}]}